    "description": "《侍神大乱战Samurai Bringer》是一款和風Roguelite动作游戏。<br>在游戏中玩家需要对抗众多武士和妖怪，提升战技，向讨伐八岐大蛇为目标进发。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重获荒神之力，挑战八岐大蛇</h2>主角荒神须佐之男为了拯救被选中活祭的栉名田而挑战八岐大蛇。<br><br>然而，他被八岐大蛇打败甚至连力量也被夺走了。<br>太阳神天照及时救了须佐之男，为了夺回力量给予须佐之男试练。<br><br>天照大人从时空的缝隙中召唤众多来自战国时代的武士和妖怪，<br>迫使他学习战斗心得來提升自我能力……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851280/extras/9707195bcb8abdcc8cc59bec5242c7a7.poster.avif?t=1740628512\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851280/extras/9707195bcb8abdcc8cc59bec5242c7a7.webm?t=1740628512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851280/extras/9707195bcb8abdcc8cc59bec5242c7a7.mp4?t=1740628512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组合各种战技，创造个人战法</h2>击败袭来的武士和妖怪来获取“战技卷轴”。<br>学习“横扫”、“突刺”和“跳跃”等新战技。<br>此外，玩家可以自由将战技组合起来，创造个人的原创动作指令。<br>如回旋斩击、火焰攻击，甚至组合多个战技发挥出连击动作。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851280/extras/82895cac5e147f58584be271365a2fa6.poster.avif?t=1740628512\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851280/extras/82895cac5e147f58584be271365a2fa6.webm?t=1740628512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851280/extras/82895cac5e147f58584be271365a2fa6.mp4?t=1740628512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >讨伐过百以上的知名猛将</h2>在主角须佐之男面前，出现织田信长、伊达政宗和真田幸村等超过百位以上传奇猛将。<br><br>击败这些猛将后，可以获得具有各种效果的武具。<br>装备武具不仅能在战斗中获得优势，还能改变须佐之男的外观。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851280/extras/7733cd837dedcf35865b977a457faf1a.poster.avif?t=1740628512\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851280/extras/7733cd837dedcf35865b977a457faf1a.webm?t=1740628512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851280/extras/7733cd837dedcf35865b977a457faf1a.mp4?t=1740628512\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不管被打败多少次都能积累武功</h2>各个阶段都是自动生成，沿途中每次都要面对不同类型的众武士和妖怪，<br>获得的战技也因而有所变化。<br>即使被打败了也并非一无所获，因为积累武功可强化须佐之男。<br>为各种战斗做好准备，向讨伐八岐大蛇为目标而进发吧！",
